## Deployment Process

### 1. Staging Deployment

```bash
# 1. Merge to develop
git checkout develop
git pull origin develop

# 2. Run tests
pnpm test

# 3. Deploy to staging
pnpm deploy:staging

# 4. Verify deployment
pnpm test:e2e:staging
```

### 2. Production Deployment

```bash
# 1. Create release branch
git checkout -b release/v1.0.0

# 2. Update version
pnpm version patch

# 3. Run tests
pnpm test
```

